@mgorny thanks for testing.

I think I deliberately didn't add it in https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/7382 because I don't think it should be in Cython master until we have access to PyMutex and critical section.

However, I think it should be available on this "preview" branch because hopefully everyone is sensible enough not know it's for testing and not for shipping. I'll push a commit to fix that shortly.
